        <div class="problem-card">
          <div class="problem-icon">üí∏</div>
          <h3>Hosting Costs Keep Rising</h3>
          <p>Premium hosting, security plugins, backup services, CDN costs‚Äîit all adds up to hundreds per month for decent performance.</p>
