        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">1</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Content Audit & Analysis</h3>
            <p>We analyze your existing site structure, identify valuable content, and create a migration roadmap that preserves SEO value.</p>
            <div class="timeline-details">
              <span>‚Ä¢ Content inventory</span>
              <span>‚Ä¢ SEO analysis</span>
              <span>‚Ä¢ Performance baseline</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
