              <span>‚Ä¢ Mobile optimization</span>
              <span>‚Ä¢ Performance improvements</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-marker">3</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Content Migration & Optimization</h3>
            <p>We transfer all your content, optimize images, and ensure nothing gets lost in translation.</p>
            <div class="timeline-details">
