          <p>Modernize outdated HTML sites with responsive design, better performance, and easier content management.</p>
          <div class="migration-includes">
            <span>‚úì Code modernization</span>
            <span>‚úì Mobile responsiveness</span>
            <span>‚úì Performance boost</span>
            <span>‚úì SEO improvements</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="migration-card">
          <h3>Shopify/WooCommerce</h3>
          <p>Migrate product catalogs and marketing pages for blazing-fast performance while keeping your e-commerce backend.</p>
          <div class="migration-includes">
            <span>‚úì Product pages</span>
            <span>‚úì Category structure</span>
            <span>‚úì Marketing content</span>
            <span>‚úì Blog migration</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="guarantee-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="guarantee">
        <h3>Migration Guarantee</h3>
        <p>We guarantee your new site will load at least 3x faster than your current site, or we'll optimize it until it does.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Escape the WordPress Trap?</h2>
      <p>Stop losing customers to slow load times. Let's migrate you to something that actually performs.</p>
      <a href="/#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Get Migration Quote</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
.service-hero {
  padding: calc(80px + var(--space-16)) 0 var(--space-16);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669 0%, #064e3b 100%);
  color: #ffffff;
  text-align: center;
}

[data-theme="dark"] .service-hero {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #047857 0%, #022c22 100%);
}

.hero-content {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.hero-title {
  font-size: clamp(var(--text-3xl), 5vw, var(--text-5xl));
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  color: #ffffff;
}

.hero-subtitle {
  font-size: var(--text-xl);
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  color: #ffffff;
  opacity: 0.95;
}

.comparison-stats {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
}

.before-after {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
  gap: var(--space-6);
  align-items: center;
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.stat-column h3 {
  font-size: var(--text-lg);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  color: #ffffff;
}

.stat-item {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  padding: var(--space-4);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
}

.stat-item.bad {
  border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
}

.stat-item.good {
  border-left: 4px solid #10b981;
}

.stat-number {
  display: block;
  font-size: var(--text-2xl);
  font-weight: 800;
  color: #ffffff;
}

.stat-label {
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  color: #ffffff;
  opacity: 0.8;
}

.arrow {
  font-size: var(--text-3xl);
  color: #ffd700;
  font-weight: bold;
}

.section-title {
  font-size: clamp(var(--text-2xl), 4vw, var(--text-4xl));
  font-weight: 700;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  color: var(--color-primary);
}

.migration-problems {
  padding: var(--space-20) 0;
  background: var(--color-white);
}

.problems-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-6);
}

.problem-card {
  background: var(--color-light-gray);
  padding: var(--space-6);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
  text-align: center;
}

[data-theme="dark"] .problem-card {
  background: var(--color-light-gray);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}

.problem-icon {
  font-size: var(--text-4xl);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
}

.problem-card h3 {
  font-size: var(--text-xl);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  color: var(--color-primary);
}

.problem-card p {
  color: var(--color-secondary);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.astro-solution {
  padding: var(--space-20) 0;
  background: var(--color-light-gray);
}

.solution-features {
  display: grid;
  gap: var(--space-8);
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.feature-item {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--space-6);
  align-items: flex-start;
  background: var(--color-white);
  padding: var(--space-6);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  border-left: 4px solid #10b981;
}

[data-theme="dark"] .feature-item {
  background: var(--color-white);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}

.feature-icon {
  font-size: var(--text-3xl);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.feature-content h3 {
  font-size: var(--text-xl);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  color: var(--color-primary);
}

.feature-content p {
  color: var(--color-secondary);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.migration-process {
  padding: var(--space-20) 0;
  background: var(--color-white);
}

.process-timeline {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  position: relative;
}

.process-timeline::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  left: 30px;
  top: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  width: 2px;
  background: var(--color-border);
}

.timeline-item {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--space-6);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  position: relative;
}

.timeline-marker {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 60px;
  height: 60px;
  background: var(--color-accent);
  color: #ffffff;
  border-radius: 50%;
  font-size: var(--text-xl);
  font-weight: 800;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

.timeline-content h3 {
  font-size: var(--text-xl);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  color: var(--color-primary);
}

.timeline-content p {
  color: var(--color-secondary);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.timeline-details {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: var(--space-2);
}

.timeline-details span {
  background: var(--color-light-gray);
  padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-3);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  color: var(--color-secondary);
}

.migration-types {
  padding: var(--space-20) 0;
  background: var(--color-light-gray);
}

.migration-options {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-6);
}

.migration-card {
  background: var(--color-white);
  padding: var(--space-6);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  text-align: center;
}

[data-theme="dark"] .migration-card {
  background: var(--color-white);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
}

.migration-card h3 {
  font-size: var(--text-xl);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  color: var(--color-primary);
}

.migration-card p {
  color: var(--color-secondary);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.migration-includes {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: var(--space-2);
  justify-content: center;
}

.migration-includes span {
  background: var(--color-light-gray);
  padding: var(--space-1) var(--space-3);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  color: var(--color-secondary);
}

.guarantee-section {
  padding: var(--space-20) 0;
  background: var(--color-white);
}

.guarantee {
  text-align: center;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1) 0%, rgba(6, 78, 59, 0.1) 100%);
  padding: var(--space-8);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  border: 2px solid #10b981;
}

.guarantee h3 {
  color: var(--color-primary);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
}

.guarantee p {
  color: var(--color-secondary);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.cta-section {
  padding: var(--space-20) 0;
  background: #1a1a2e;
  color: #ffffff;
  text-align: center;
}

[data-theme="dark"] .cta-section {
  background: #0f172a;
}

.cta-section h2 {
  font-size: clamp(var(--text-2xl), 4vw, var(--text-4xl));
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  color: #ffffff;
}

.cta-section p {
  font-size: var(--text-lg);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  color: #ffffff;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .before-after {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .arrow {
    transform: rotate(90deg);
  }
  
  .feature-item {
    flex-direction: column;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .timeline-item {
    flex-direction: column;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .process-timeline::before {
    display: none;
  }
}
</style>